Package universitysystem.courses

Class Course

java.lang.Object
universitysystem.courses.Course
public class Course extends Object
class `Course` presents an academic course offered in a university. It includes details such as course code, title, description, credits, and other relevant information. Courses can have prerequisites, associated faculties, lessons, and registration status.
